            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4">
                <h5>Preserve beautifully, deliver sophisticatedly</h5>
                <%= image_tag "for_use/icons/handbag.png", class: "mission-icon" %>
                <p>Natural fibers have distinctive characteristics and that's how we make the best use of it. We cater to the designs
                that are timeless and natural so you will not only look beautiful, but also different and unique</p>
            </div>
        </div>
